description:
&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen to join the Barts Health NHS Trust Supply Chain Team, as we are recruiting for 2 x Band 5 Materials Manager on 12 Month Fixed Term based at Royal London Hospital (cross cover to other Barts sites will be required) from Monday-Friday, 8am-4pm (37.5 hours per week). The post holder will be responsible for providing a day-to-day materials management operational service to wards and departments in the Trust as part of the overall Procurement Team. He/she will be responsible for processing of stock and non-stock items via a personal data capture unit on wards and clinical areas and be the local Customer focus for assistance and advice. The post holder will support the development and implementation of the Barts Health Supply Chain Transformation strategy, with particular emphasis on Atticus Inventory Management System deployment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Melanie Doherty melanie.doherty3@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
